==Geography==
* State - [[Pernambuco]] * Region - [[Sertão]] Pernambucano * Boundaries - [[Exu, Pernambuco|Exu]] and [[Moreilândia]] ('''N'''); [[Parnamirim, Pernambuco|Parnamirim]] ('''S'''); [[Serrita]] ('''E'''); [[Bodocó]] ('''W'''). * Area - 521.86&nbsp;km² * Elevation - 447 m * Hidrography - [[Brigida River]] * Vegetation - [[Caatinga]] * Clima - [[semi arid]] - ([[Sertão]]) hot * Annual average temperature - 25.4 c * Distance to [[Recife]] - 592&nbsp;km
==Economy==
The main economic activities in '''Granito''' are based in [[agribusiness]], especially creation of [[cattle]], [[sheep]], [[goats]], [[donkeys]], [[chickens]]; and plantations of [[maize|corn]].
